{
  "video_id": "DVoNi3ypFA8",
  "title": "Christian Show | Testimony of the Faith of a Christian | \"Escaping the Cage\" (2018 Crosstalk)",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 1769.0,
      "end_time": 3303.0,
      "text": "﻿Hey? Xiaolan? (Hi!)"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 3304.0,
      "end_time": 5538.0,
      "text": "I haven&#39;t seen you in a while. Where&#39;ve you been?"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 5806.0,
      "end_time": 8440.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve been in \"jail\" for the past month."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 8442.0,
      "end_time": 9309.0,
      "text": "What!"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 9310.0,
      "end_time": 11770.0,
      "text": "Were you reported for spreading the gospel?"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 11780.0,
      "end_time": 12112.0,
      "text": "Nope."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 12113.0,
      "end_time": 13546.0,
      "text": "Were you followed to a meeting?"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 13547.0,
      "end_time": 14414.0,
      "text": "Nope."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 14415.0,
      "end_time": 16181.0,
      "text": "Was your phone monitored? (No.)"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 16183.0,
      "end_time": 17183.0,
      "text": "Oh, then were you …"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 17184.0,
      "end_time": 17584.0,
      "text": "No."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 17585.0,
      "end_time": 20754.0,
      "text": "Hey, hey, hey, hey, so what exactly happened?"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 20755.0,
      "end_time": 23890.0,
      "text": "The \"jail\" I&#39;m talking about is my home."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 23900.0,
      "end_time": 25225.0,
      "text": "My dad kept me locked up at home."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 25226.0,
      "end_time": 27460.0,
      "text": "He didn&#39;t find out you believe in God, did he?"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 27461.0,
      "end_time": 28828.0,
      "text": "Don&#39;t even ask."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 28829.0,
      "end_time": 29696.0,
      "text": "What happened?"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 29697.0,
      "end_time": 34330.0,
      "text": "He found out I believe in Almighty God and he pushes me to stop every day."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 34340.0,
      "end_time": 35468.0,
      "text": "He never lets up!"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 35469.0,
      "end_time": 39239.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not easy believing in God when you live with a Communist Party official."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 39240.0,
      "end_time": 40573.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re not kidding!"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 40574.0,
      "end_time": 43476.0,
      "text": "My father, secretary of political and legal affairs. (Yeah?)"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 43477.0,
      "end_time": 44943.0,
      "text": "In charge of religions."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 45379.0,
      "end_time": 47647.0,
      "text": "Would he ever agree to me believing in God?"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 47648.0,
      "end_time": 49482.0,
      "text": "The Chinese Communist Party (Yes?)"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 49483.0,
      "end_time": 53419.0,
      "text": "says that if national cadres or their relatives believe in God,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 53421.0,
      "end_time": 55321.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re fired the second it&#39;s found out!"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 55322.0,
      "end_time": 55989.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s right."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 55990.0,
      "end_time": 57791.0,
      "text": "You&#39;ll have to believe in secret."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 58359.0,
      "end_time": 61261.0,
      "text": "That day I came home after my meeting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 61262.0,
      "end_time": 62996.0,
      "text": "and I saw an angry look on his face."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 62997.0,
      "end_time": 64960.0,
      "text": "What happened?"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 64364.00000000001,
      "end_time": 67767.0,
      "text": "He found the book of God&#39;s word I had hid in my dresser."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 67768.0,
      "end_time": 71171.0,
      "text": "It looks like she has a domestic spiritual battle coming up."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 72840.0,
      "end_time": 75775.0,
      "text": "\"Xiaolan, do you believe in Almighty God?"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 76544.0,
      "end_time": 78478.0,
      "text": "Did you just come back from a meeting?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 78712.0,
      "end_time": 80380.0,
      "text": "\"Yes, what&#39;s wrong?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 80748.0,
      "end_time": 81848.0,
      "text": "\"What&#39;s wrong!"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 82116.0,
      "end_time": 86219.0,
      "text": "The central government issued many documents demanding that we suppress religious belief."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 86220.0,
      "end_time": 88855.0,
      "text": "They want to fully eliminate house churches,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 88856.0,
      "end_time": 90957.0,
      "text": "especially The Church of Almighty God,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 90958.0,
      "end_time": 94194.0,
      "text": "they won&#39;t stop until they stamp it out completely!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 94195.0,
      "end_time": 97229.0,
      "text": "He is implementing the central government&#39;s guidelines at home!"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 98980.0,
      "end_time": 102350.0,
      "text": "\"The CCP is brutal with anybody who believes in God."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 102360.0,
      "end_time": 106239.0,
      "text": "If you dare believe in God in China, you must have a death wish!"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 106574.0,
      "end_time": 110760.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m warning you, you better quit believing in Almighty God!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 110770.0,
      "end_time": 115480.0,
      "text": "How the CCP takes \"care\" of things is always worse than you&#39;d imagine."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 115490.0,
      "end_time": 116916.0,
      "text": "Your dad is right about that."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 116917.0,
      "end_time": 120720.0,
      "text": "I can understand his fear of me being arrested and going to jail."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 120721.0,
      "end_time": 122555.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s natural that he&#39;d worry."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 122556.0,
      "end_time": 126960.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s why I had to use reason and sentiment to change his mind."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 126961.0,
      "end_time": 130295.0,
      "text": "Right, just lay out the facts and explain things to him."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 130297.0,
      "end_time": 132732.0,
      "text": "I went to the kitchen to get him a cup of tea. (Yes?)"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 134502.0,
      "end_time": 135401.0,
      "text": "\"Dad,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 136370.0,
      "end_time": 141140.0,
      "text": "remember how I was so focused on myself before I started believing in God?"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 141141.0,
      "end_time": 144109.0,
      "text": "I spent all my time amusing myself, wasting my life away,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 144411.0,
      "end_time": 146450.0,
      "text": "I was selfish and stubborn."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 146447.0,
      "end_time": 148448.0,
      "text": "I caused you and Mom a lot of worry.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 148449.0,
      "end_time": 150350.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s just how young people are."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 150351.0,
      "end_time": 153586.0,
      "text": "\"Then I believed in God and read Almighty God&#39;s words,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 153587.0,
      "end_time": 155210.0,
      "text": "I understood the truth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 155220.0,
      "end_time": 157550.0,
      "text": "and saw the world&#39;s darkness and evil clearly.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 157570.0,
      "end_time": 157923.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s right!"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 157925.0,
      "end_time": 161394.0,
      "text": "\"I practice according to God&#39;s word and want to be an honest person,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 161395.0,
      "end_time": 164731.0,
      "text": "with normal humanity, walking the correct path."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 164732.0,
      "end_time": 167200.0,
      "text": "This was all because Almighty God saved me!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 167201.0,
      "end_time": 169769.0,
      "text": "And was his attitude better after you told him that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 169770.0,
      "end_time": 171170.0,
      "text": "My dad said, (Yes?)"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 172506.0,
      "end_time": 176442.0,
      "text": "\"I admit you&#39;ve changed since believing in God."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 176443.0,
      "end_time": 178440.0,
      "text": "I know believing in God is good.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 178450.0,
      "end_time": 178911.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s right."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 178913.0,
      "end_time": 181414.0,
      "text": "\"But the Communist Party doesn&#39;t allow belief in God!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 181415.0,
      "end_time": 183917.0,
      "text": "You&#39;ll be persecuted if you&#39;re a believer."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 183918.0,
      "end_time": 185218.0,
      "text": "\"Xiaolan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 185219.0,
      "end_time": 186619.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re too young,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 186620.0,
      "end_time": 189722.0,
      "text": "and you don&#39;t understand the Communist Party."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 189723.0,
      "end_time": 194930.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re atheist and they hate believers more than anyone."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 194940.0,
      "end_time": 196829.0,
      "text": "Sometimes you go to jail, sometimes they kill you!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 196830.0,
      "end_time": 198698.0,
      "text": "And they don&#39;t even need a reason."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 199300.0,
      "end_time": 202435.0,
      "text": "\"If they arrest you, I won&#39;t be able to help you."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 202436.0,
      "end_time": 205438.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m forbidding you from believing for your own good!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 205439.0,
      "end_time": 206739.0,
      "text": "What did you say?"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 207641.0,
      "end_time": 210510.0,
      "text": "\"Dad, I know everything you&#39;re telling me.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 211145.0,
      "end_time": 212579.0,
      "text": "\"But you still believe?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 214480.0,
      "end_time": 217250.0,
      "text": "\"Dad, the world is so dark and evil today.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 217251.0,
      "end_time": 217951.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s right."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 217952.0,
      "end_time": 220850.0,
      "text": "\"People have been corrupted so deeply."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 220721.0,
      "end_time": 223122.0,
      "text": "If we don&#39;t believe in God and repent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 223123.0,
      "end_time": 225257.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ll be destroyed in the disaster.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 225259.0,
      "end_time": 228194.0,
      "text": "Mankind is corrupt and needs God&#39;s salvation."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 228195.0,
      "end_time": 230897.0,
      "text": "\"Alright, enough. I don&#39;t believe any of that!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 230898.0,
      "end_time": 232498.0,
      "text": "A typical atheist."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 232499.0,
      "end_time": 235902.0,
      "text": "\"I&#39;m a Communist Party official, they pay my salary,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 235903.0,
      "end_time": 237804.0,
      "text": "and I work for them."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 238672.0,
      "end_time": 242508.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s forbidden for Christians to exist in a Communist member&#39;s family!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 242509.0,
      "end_time": 246212.0,
      "text": "The CCP sure has turned your dad into a loyal party member!"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 246213.0,
      "end_time": 247647.0,
      "text": "Yes, they have!"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 247648.0,
      "end_time": 249482.0,
      "text": "And as soon as I heard my dad&#39;s words, I …"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 249483.0,
      "end_time": 250450.0,
      "text": "Were you wavering?"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 250718.0,
      "end_time": 252918.0,
      "text": "I told him exactly what I thought. (Oh?)"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 253921.0,
      "end_time": 254754.0,
      "text": "\"Dad,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 254755.0,
      "end_time": 257550.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ll listen to you in everything else,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 257570.0,
      "end_time": 260927.0,
      "text": "but in the matter of belief, I have my views and position."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 260928.0,
      "end_time": 263229.0,
      "text": "No matter what you say, I&#39;ll believe in God.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 263230.0,
      "end_time": 265565.0,
      "text": "Her statement is clear and her position is firm."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 265566.0,
      "end_time": 267967.0,
      "text": "I might have been clear, but my dad couldn&#39;t accept it."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 267968.0,
      "end_time": 268768.0,
      "text": "Why not?"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 269370.0,
      "end_time": 272405.0,
      "text": "\"I spent all that time talking, and you didn&#39;t hear any of it!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 272406.0,
      "end_time": 273673.0,
      "text": "He&#39;s angry now."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 273674.0,
      "end_time": 277477.0,
      "text": "\"If you don&#39;t listen to me, not only will you end up in jail,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 277478.0,
      "end_time": 279112.0,
      "text": "but I&#39;ll lose my job."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 279980.0,
      "end_time": 282448.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re my daughter! Do what I say!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 282449.0,
      "end_time": 286319.0,
      "text": "Communist Party officials also use their power to oppress at home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 286320.0,
      "end_time": 287986.0,
      "text": "even on their own children!"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 287988.0,
      "end_time": 290923.0,
      "text": "Just when he finished speaking, I heard a bang!"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 290924.0,
      "end_time": 291957.0,
      "text": "What was it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 291959.0,
      "end_time": 293793.0,
      "text": "He slammed the door and left."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 293794.0,
      "end_time": 295460.0,
      "text": "And then I was under lock and key."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 295462.0,
      "end_time": 296863.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s terrible."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 296864.0,
      "end_time": 298664.0,
      "text": "No, it wasn&#39;t. (It wasn&#39;t?)"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 298666.0,
      "end_time": 302168.0,
      "text": "My dad and my mom put me under 24-hour surveillance!"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 302169.0,
      "end_time": 304300.0,
      "text": "They really feel like watching you!"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 304471.0,
      "end_time": 307307.0,
      "text": "One day, I had a meeting, so I told my dad …"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 307308.0,
      "end_time": 307940.0,
      "text": "Yes?"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 308909.0,
      "end_time": 311711.0,
      "text": "\"Dad, I have something to do, I&#39;m going out.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 311712.0,
      "end_time": 312611.0,
      "text": "Did he let you?"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 312613.0,
      "end_time": 313446.0,
      "text": "Yes!"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 313447.0,
      "end_time": 314514.0,
      "text": "He&#39;s your father,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 314515.0,
      "end_time": 316382.0,
      "text": "he doesn&#39;t wanna be too hard on you."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 316383.0,
      "end_time": 317490.0,
      "text": "Oh really?"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 317510.0,
      "end_time": 317550.0,
      "text": "Huh?"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 317851.0,
      "end_time": 319886.0,
      "text": "He was very hard on me!"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 319887.0,
      "end_time": 321154.0,
      "text": "What happened then?"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 321155.0,
      "end_time": 323789.0,
      "text": "My dad, while reading the newspaper, said, (Yeah?)"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 324391.0,
      "end_time": 326359.0,
      "text": "\"You&#39;re her mother, you go with her.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 326360.0,
      "end_time": 329696.0,
      "text": "Oh! So, he made your mom become your bodyguard?"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 329697.0,
      "end_time": 330763.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s right!"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 330764.0,
      "end_time": 334167.0,
      "text": "My mom watched me during the day and stayed with me at night. (Wow!)"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 334168.0,
      "end_time": 335902.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t have any freedom at all."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 335903.0,
      "end_time": 337537.0,
      "text": "Like a bird in a cage."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 338500.0,
      "end_time": 341441.0,
      "text": "I couldn&#39;t go to meetings or see my brothers and sisters."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 341442.0,
      "end_time": 344444.0,
      "text": "It was absolute torture! Awful!"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 344912.0,
      "end_time": 346145.0,
      "text": "I wanted—(Hey!)"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 346847.0,
      "end_time": 348847.0,
      "text": "You didn&#39;t do anything crazy, did you?"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 348849.0,
      "end_time": 350316.0,
      "text": "I wanted to sing."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 351318.0,
      "end_time": 352385.0,
      "text": "Then sing."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 367201.0,
      "end_time": 368101.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s right."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 381348.0,
      "end_time": 385184.0,
      "text": "Hey, you can&#39;t just suffer. Pray to God!"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 385185.0,
      "end_time": 388221.0,
      "text": "Right, relying on God is the wisest thing to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 388222.0,
      "end_time": 389287.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s right!"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 389289.0,
      "end_time": 391890.0,
      "text": "I prayed, and read a passage of God&#39;s word."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 391892.0,
      "end_time": 393826.0,
      "text": "Well, share it with us."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 409910.0,
      "end_time": 410743.0,
      "text": "Amen!"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 411440.0,
      "end_time": 413378.0,
      "text": "Listening to God&#39;s word gives us faith!"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 413380.0,
      "end_time": 414447.0,
      "text": "Exactly!"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 414448.0,
      "end_time": 419850.0,
      "text": "Even though I lost my church life, and couldn&#39;t see my brothers and sisters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 419860.0,
      "end_time": 420486.0,
      "text": "God was with me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 420487.0,
      "end_time": 423220.0,
      "text": "leading me and making my faith stronger. (Yes.)"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 423230.0,
      "end_time": 424557.0,
      "text": "I grew spiritually."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 424558.0,
      "end_time": 426192.0,
      "text": "Thanks to God&#39;s guidance."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 426193.0,
      "end_time": 428426.0,
      "text": "My dad could control my movements,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 428428.0,
      "end_time": 431630.0,
      "text": "but he couldn&#39;t stop my heart from following God."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 431365.0,
      "end_time": 434567.0,
      "text": "At home I could still read God&#39;s word and be near God."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 434568.0,
      "end_time": 437169.0,
      "text": "This is the kind of witness Christians should have!"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 438672.0,
      "end_time": 441340.0,
      "text": "But just after I had managed to calm down,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 441341.0,
      "end_time": 443576.0,
      "text": "a huge wave came along and struck me."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 443577.0,
      "end_time": 445440.0,
      "text": "What huge wave?"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 445450.0,
      "end_time": 447146.0,
      "text": "One day, my dad wasn&#39;t at home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 447147.0,
      "end_time": 449582.0,
      "text": "and I was secretly listening to hymns of God&#39;s word."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 449583.0,
      "end_time": 450283.0,
      "text": "And?"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 450284.0,
      "end_time": 452450.0,
      "text": "Suddenly, the door of my \"jail\" burst open."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 452452.0,
      "end_time": 453119.0,
      "text": "What?"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 453821.0,
      "end_time": 455988.0,
      "text": "Oh, the door of my room."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 455989.0,
      "end_time": 456888.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s your dad?"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 456890.0,
      "end_time": 457556.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s correct."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 457558.0,
      "end_time": 458424.0,
      "text": "Oh no!"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 459293.0,
      "end_time": 462228.0,
      "text": "\"Xiaolan, are you still singing those hymns?"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 462229.0,
      "end_time": 464964.0,
      "text": "There was a new policy from the central government,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 464965.0,
      "end_time": 468340.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re starting a national &#39;One Hundred Day Battle,&#39;"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 468350.0,
      "end_time": 470169.0,
      "text": "involving police and armed forces"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 470170.0,
      "end_time": 473639.0,
      "text": "to do a blanket search and roundup of all believers in Almighty God.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 473640.0,
      "end_time": 476842.0,
      "text": "The CCP&#39;s tides of oppression of God&#39;s chosen people"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 476844.0,
      "end_time": 478945.0,
      "text": "come in one wave after another."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 479446.0,
      "end_time": 481647.0,
      "text": "\"Don&#39;t you see how bad this situation is?"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 482616.0,
      "end_time": 486519.0,
      "text": "The central government wants to dig out every last believer in Almighty God.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 486520.0,
      "end_time": 487486.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s awful!"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 487988.0,
      "end_time": 491724.0,
      "text": "\"Listen, you will never go to another meeting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 492250.0,
      "end_time": 495695.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re not reading The Word Appears in the Flesh anymore either!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 495696.0,
      "end_time": 500466.0,
      "text": "The CCP oppresses believers to the point that they can&#39;t even read God&#39;s word at home."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 500467.0,
      "end_time": 502435.0,
      "text": "I can&#39;t tell you how furious I was!"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 502436.0,
      "end_time": 503536.0,
      "text": "Of course you were!"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 503537.0,
      "end_time": 505438.0,
      "text": "I remembered God&#39;s word, (What?)"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 522990.0,
      "end_time": 528600.0,
      "text": "The CCP persecutes Christians while declaring China&#39;s \"religious freedom\" abroad."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 528610.0,
      "end_time": 529829.0,
      "text": "Nothing could be more shameless!"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 530464.0,
      "end_time": 533499.0,
      "text": "Seeing the CCP&#39;s true face of resistance to God"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 533500.0,
      "end_time": 535868.0,
      "text": "only strengthened my faith that I should follow God."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 535869.0,
      "end_time": 537360.0,
      "text": "Thanks be to God!"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 537370.0,
      "end_time": 539539.0,
      "text": "I was determined, so I said to my dad, (Yeah?)"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 540741.0,
      "end_time": 543776.0,
      "text": "\"Dad, you can ask me to do anything else,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 543777.0,
      "end_time": 546879.0,
      "text": "but I will never give up belief in God.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 546880.0,
      "end_time": 549248.0,
      "text": "That must have just made him way angrier!"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 549249.0,
      "end_time": 550149.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s right."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 550150.0,
      "end_time": 552151.0,
      "text": "My dad stood right up and raised his hand."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 552152.0,
      "end_time": 553552.0,
      "text": "To hit you? (I closed my eyes.)"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 553553.0,
      "end_time": 554987.0,
      "text": "Waiting to be struck."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 554988.0,
      "end_time": 556222.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s what I thought too."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 556223.0,
      "end_time": 557356.0,
      "text": "So, what happened?"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 557891.0,
      "end_time": 560159.0,
      "text": "\"I&#39;ll say it one last time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 560160.0,
      "end_time": 562528.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s either God or your parents?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 562529.0,
      "end_time": 563596.0,
      "text": "What&#39;d you say?"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 564531.0,
      "end_time": 566732.0,
      "text": "\"Dad, I want both.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 566733.0,
      "end_time": 568434.0,
      "text": "And yet you can&#39;t have it."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 568669.0,
      "end_time": 570202.0,
      "text": "\"You need to make a choice!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 570203.0,
      "end_time": 571737.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re making this so hard."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 572205.0,
      "end_time": 573472.0,
      "text": "Exactly."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 573874.0,
      "end_time": 576475.0,
      "text": "On one side the parents who raised me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 576476.0,
      "end_time": 580279.0,
      "text": "on the other the God who gave me breath and life."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 580280.0,
      "end_time": 582180.0,
      "text": "It was a hard choice for me."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 582182.0,
      "end_time": 583783.0,
      "text": "Then pray to God!"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 584251.0,
      "end_time": 584983.0,
      "text": "Right!"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 584985.0,
      "end_time": 587286.0,
      "text": "After I prayed, I said to my dad,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 588121.0,
      "end_time": 592580.0,
      "text": "\"Dad, I believe in Almighty God, and that will never change.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 592590.0,
      "end_time": 593959.0,
      "text": "This is the right choice to make."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 593961.0,
      "end_time": 595661.0,
      "text": "But my dad wouldn&#39;t have it."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 595662.0,
      "end_time": 597263.0,
      "text": "He started slamming things around."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 597264.0,
      "end_time": 598300.0,
      "text": "What was he doing?"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 598310.0,
      "end_time": 600232.0,
      "text": "Smashing my phone and my computer."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 600233.0,
      "end_time": 600800.0,
      "text": "What?"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 600801.0,
      "end_time": 601867.0,
      "text": "Then picking up a lighter …"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 601868.0,
      "end_time": 602702.0,
      "text": "To start a fire?"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 602703.0,
      "end_time": 604470.0,
      "text": "To burn my book of God&#39;s words. (This …)"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 604471.0,
      "end_time": 606205.0,
      "text": "Without even thinking I grabbed for it."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 606206.0,
      "end_time": 607273.0,
      "text": "What happened?"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 609209.0,
      "end_time": 612780.0,
      "text": "Whack, whack, slapped in the face."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 612446.0,
      "end_time": 615548.0,
      "text": "Oh no! He actually hit you."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 616383.0,
      "end_time": 622788.0,
      "text": "I looked up at my father&#39;s familiar, yet strange and ruthless face."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 623991.0,
      "end_time": 627560.0,
      "text": "I felt like I had been doused with cold water."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 628128.0,
      "end_time": 630960.0,
      "text": "Completely discouraged!"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 630797.0,
      "end_time": 635301.0,
      "text": "\"So you&#39;re all grown up now? You&#39;re a big girl?"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 635869.0,
      "end_time": 638738.0,
      "text": "If you won&#39;t listen to me, then you&#39;re not my daughter!"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 638739.0,
      "end_time": 639872.0,
      "text": "Get out!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 639873.0,
      "end_time": 641307.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s ruthless!"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 643977.0,
      "end_time": 644944.0,
      "text": "\"Dad,"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 646146.0,
      "end_time": 650716.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re really sending me away just because I believe in God?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 650717.0,
      "end_time": 651684.0,
      "text": "Really!"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 653860.0,
      "end_time": 655421.0,
      "text": "When my mom saw how angry my dad was,"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 655422.0,
      "end_time": 656455.0,
      "text": "she got frantic."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 656456.0,
      "end_time": 656956.0,
      "text": "Oh?"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 656957.0,
      "end_time": 659158.0,
      "text": "She grabbed him and pulled him out of the room."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 659159.0,
      "end_time": 662995.0,
      "text": "I heard the door slam, and I was locked inside again."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 663230.0,
      "end_time": 664897.0,
      "text": "She was locked up again."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 665499.0,
      "end_time": 666966.0,
      "text": "I had never imagined"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 666967.0,
      "end_time": 670269.0,
      "text": "that the father who once loved me would ever see me as the enemy."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 670270.0,
      "end_time": 673606.0,
      "text": "He jailed me in my own home, and completely cut me off."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 673607.0,
      "end_time": 676740.0,
      "text": "The CCP caused this evil."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 676760.0,
      "end_time": 680312.0,
      "text": "All I wanted to do was believe in God, read God&#39;s word, and walk the correct path."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 680313.0,
      "end_time": 681213.0,
      "text": "Right."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 681214.0,
      "end_time": 686385.0,
      "text": "Why is that one simple little wish so difficult to realize in China?"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 686386.0,
      "end_time": 689622.0,
      "text": "This is the plea of every single Christian in China!"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 723290.0,
      "end_time": 726920.0,
      "text": "The CCP controls the Chinese people."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 726930.0,
      "end_time": 728930.0,
      "text": "It doesn&#39;t give them any freedom,"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 728950.0,
      "end_time": 730496.0,
      "text": "and doesn&#39;t allow them to even believe in God."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 730497.0,
      "end_time": 731863.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s right!"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 731865.0,
      "end_time": 736368.0,
      "text": "China as ruled by the CCP really is a demonic prison!"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 736369.0,
      "end_time": 738938.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s hard to believe in God in China!"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 739406.0,
      "end_time": 741674.0,
      "text": "The CCP may control our bodies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 741675.0,
      "end_time": 745377.0,
      "text": "but they can&#39;t control our determination to believe in and follow God!"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 745378.0,
      "end_time": 746312.0,
      "text": "Amen!"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 746713.0,
      "end_time": 748814.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s when I looked for a bedsheet."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 748815.0,
      "end_time": 749515.0,
      "text": "What for?"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 749516.0,
      "end_time": 750382.0,
      "text": "To make a rope."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 750383.0,
      "end_time": 751584.0,
      "text": "You can&#39;t mean you&#39;d …"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 751818.0,
      "end_time": 754530.0,
      "text": "I made a rope from the bedsheet"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 754540.0,
      "end_time": 756988.0,
      "text": "so that I could sneak out when my mom was asleep!"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 757691.0,
      "end_time": 760259.0,
      "text": "She was really pushed to the brink!"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 760260.0,
      "end_time": 763763.0,
      "text": "Late at night, when I saw her asleep,"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 763764.0,
      "end_time": 765865.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t want to leave,"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 765866.0,
      "end_time": 768701.0,
      "text": "the tears streamed down my face."
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 768702.0,
      "end_time": 771370.0,
      "text": "Leaving her mother, becoming her father&#39;s enemy."
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 771371.0,
      "end_time": 773739.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s all because of the CCP!"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 774207.0,
      "end_time": 776976.0,
      "text": "I wiped the tears from my eyes, went to the window,"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 776977.0,
      "end_time": 780579.0,
      "text": "tied one end of the rope to the window and the other to my waist."
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 780580.0,
      "end_time": 781714.0,
      "text": "And now what?"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 781715.0,
      "end_time": 784150.0,
      "text": "I climbed out the window, grabbed the rope,"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 784151.0,
      "end_time": 785550.0,
      "text": "and slid right down."
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 785552.0,
      "end_time": 787553.0,
      "text": "Hey, she&#39;s free!"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 787554.0,
      "end_time": 790356.0,
      "text": "Yes! God gave me the faith and the strength"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 790357.0,
      "end_time": 792240.0,
      "text": "to escape from my cage!"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 792250.0,
      "end_time": 794160.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s all thanks to God&#39;s guidance!"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 794161.0,
      "end_time": 797290.0,
      "text": "And now I can go to meetings with my brothers and sisters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 797300.0,
      "end_time": 799131.0,
      "text": "spread the gospel, and testify to God!"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 799132.0,
      "end_time": 800699.0,
      "text": "Thanks be to God!"
    }
  ]
}